To build the programs, simply run make:

   .../hw5$  make

All three programs have usage statements. Examples are as follows

   .../hw5$  ./eigP -e 1e-4 -v8 -f sample.dat

   # will find the 8 evecs with largest evals from 
   #    input file sample.dat with error < 1e-4
   # eigenvalues and eigenvectors are written to respective *.out files
   
